<plot>Ava is a young courageous Dutch woman who flees Freiburg, Germany where she is a university student and picking up her younger brother, escapes to Arnhem, Holland with a young girl they find. Arnhem however has been heavily bombed. Ava however is determined to survive and sets up home inside a former tailor's shop. Two years later, befriended by Allied soldiers, the three finally leave to a new life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052225</url></doc>
